videos.headline: Ovi describes 'great feeling' of beating Penguins
videos.description: Alex Ovechkin joins SVP to discuss eliminating the Penguins and moving forward for more.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Ovi describes 'great feeling' of beating Penguins) 2018/05/07 ESHEET SVP SC

videos.headline: Game 6 loss stings for Crosby
videos.description: Sidney Crosby notes the Penguins haven't had a losing feeling in the playoffs in a while and how fine the line is between winning and losing.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Game 6 loss stings for Crosby) 2018/05/07 ESHEET
